contents: Okay, so move the carrot up one square
Take the pyrex measuring cup (with the handle) and move it down one
Water bottle, move to the right one square
And the chair, move it left one square
The plane, move it to the right one square
The glasses, move to the right one square
The barrel, move it down one
And the saxophone, move it up one
The comb, move it up one
And the mouse, up one as well
Feather, to the left one square
